# === LIGHTWEIGHT RESULTS WORTH KEEPING ===
# Override ignored extensions for small summary/metadata files that communicate results.
#README and markdown files are kept by default, so we whitelist specific data/config files:

# Metadata and summary JSONs
!*.json
!**/*.json

# Summary tables (small CSVs with results, metadata, diagnostics)
!*_summary.csv
!*_summary.md
!**/*_summary.csv
!**/*_summary.md
!*_metadata.csv
!*_metadata.json
!**/*_metadata.csv
!**/*_metadata.json
!*_metadata.txt

# Data audit and EDA results
!*_audit.csv
!*_audit.json
!*_eda.csv
!*_eda.md
!feature_build/
!feature_build/**
!audit/
!audit/**
!01_data_audit/
!01_data_audit/**
!02_eda/
!02_eda/**

# Plots and visualizations
!*.png
!*.jpg
!*.jpeg

# Key output/result directories for review
!outputs/
!TransResults/
!**/README.md

TransformersSection/TransResults/12_threshold_tuning_review/what_changed.md
TransformersSection/TransResults/12_threshold_tuning_review/before_vs_after_summary.md
